    "text": "The naval and fishing communities are requested to be attentive to the future forecasts and bulletins issued by the Department of Meteorology in this regard. Condition of Rain: Showers or thundershowers will occur at times in the sea areas around the island. Winds: Winds will be southwesterly. Wind speed will be (25-35) kmph. Wind speed can increase up to 50 kmph at times in the sea areas off the coast extending from Puttalam to Hambantota via Colombo and Galle. State of Sea: The sea areas off the coasts extending from Puttalam to Hambantota via Colombo and Galle will be rough at times. The other sea areas around the island can be moderate.",
